{"tid":1442507,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(重開)[純學術討論] 抗爭者/遊擊隊聖經 - Anarchist Cookbook","createTime":"2019-08-11T03:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T03:55:45.000Z","uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7d2c2c1333e051c5ea37c6190ea5d37471727f0c","tid":1442507,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">注 : 此post為純學術討論, 並不鼓吹任何非法行為</span><br />\n<br />\n簡介<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1024235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1024235&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU0XpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=d1c32db9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1024235&h=d864fc99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1024235</a><br />\n下載link<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdn.preterhuman.net/texts/terrorism_and_pyrotechnics/explosives/MISC/Anarchist%20Cookbook%20-%20William%20Powell.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.preterhuman.net%2Ftexts%2Fterrorism_and_pyrotechnics%2Fexplosives%2FMISC%2FAnarchist%2520Cookbook%2520-%2520William%2520Powell.pdf&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU0XpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=46365d7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.preterhuman.net/texts/terrorism_and_pyrotechnics/explosives/MISC/Anarchist%20Cookbook%20-%20William%20Powell.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有巴打話之前太多字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯有整個精華版<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點 :</span></span><br />\nChapter 3:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">催淚氣治療</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXGLUPY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXGLUPY.png&h=baa22d9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先用礦物油(<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">即BB油</span></strong>) 塗抹皮膚(如果無既用清水都得), <span style=\"color: red;\">再用酒精抹一次, , 催淚氣造成既皮膚灼痛感會大大縮短</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GhVkJMa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhVkJMa.png&h=4210d548&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一個source都係大同小異, 不過佢建議用植物油代替BB油都可以. <span style=\"color: red;\">重點都係第一次沖洗後要再用酒精抹一次</span><br />\n<br />\n注: 內文有提到可以用弱酸洗眼, 不過另一個source唔建議, 所以洗眼都係只建議清水<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">路障</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WSj9B7p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSj9B7p.png&h=33a89cc2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n工兵系同學可以參考<br />\n用一條高強度既cable, 橫跨馬路咁拉去兩邊燈柱/樹, 只要拉得夠恆同埋條cable夠韌, 架車就會俾條cable跣去撞落燈柱, 想陰濕D既可以先噴黑條cable, 夜晚更難睇到<br />\n<br />\nChapter 4:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">初階火魔法(雞尾酒)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RUemtgB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRUemtgB.png&h=7d4afbac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雞尾酒製作應該係<span style=\"color: red;\">白電油同油(潤滑油or食油, 潤滑油較好)用2:1比例混合</span><br />\n因為電油優點係易燃, 缺點係易揮發,不耐燒<br />\n油就啱啱相反,燃點高但持續時間高<br />\n兩者混合可互補長短<br />\n正如BBQ透爐一樣, 先用炭精(白電油)起火, 再點著耐燒既炭(油), 個火先夠大<br />\n加入油仲可以有粘附效果, 因為油係比較杰<br />\n<br />\n本書仲有其他更深入內容, 包括各類自製武器, <span style=\"color: red;\">自製催淚魔法</span>, <span style=\"color: red;\">高階火魔法</span>如黑火藥煉製以至<span style=\"color: red;\">大魔導士級火魔法</span>如TNT製作等<br />\n但內容比較複雜深奧, 有興趣既同學可以睇書自修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家重拾書本, 快樂學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90ce418b5bc914c5707878024254c1598591676","tid":1442507,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc3822e32b288df949585e707323d6797986be94","tid":1442507,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:55:45.000Z","msg":"721"}]}